Server Monetization Exception:

Running RuinedCollections on a monetized Minecraft server is allowed. This
license only blocks selling the plugin itself, its source code, its jar file,
modified builds, forks, or direct access to download it. Server owners may
monetize their servers while using this plugin, as long as they are not selling
RuinedCollections itself and they follow all applicable Minecraft, Mojang,
